{"article_id":"BD4BZPZp1bYXPNpa","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The U.S. , Iran and five world powers on Thursday reached a preliminary deal","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"designed to contain Iran ' s nuclear program , one","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"that would restrict Iran ' s ability to enrich uranium","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"and subject it to international inspections ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"but which also would gradually remove harsh economic sanctions from the Islamic Republic .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"The agreement ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"if it holds ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"could prove to be President Barack Obama ' s biggest foreign policy achievement , a success","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"stemming from his conviction","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"that it ' s worth engaging even longtime adversaries such as Tehran .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"But","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"while the framework won praise for its surprising level of detail ,","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"it failed to quell sharp skepticism from many Republicans as well as Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"\" It is a good deal , \"","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Obama declared Thursday ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"calling it \" a historic understanding with Iran","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"which ,","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"if implemented ,","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"will prevent it from obtaining a nuclear weapon .","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"\" I am convinced","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"if this framework leads to a final deal ,","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"it will make our country and the world safer , \"","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"Obama said in a appearance at the White House Rose Garden .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"The deal ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"unveiled in Lausanne , Switzerland ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"would \" cut off every pathway","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"that Iran could take","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"to develop a nuclear weapon . \"","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"Obama struck a confident tone ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"directly engaging potential critics","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"including Netanyahu and Republicans in Congress .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"Pointing to the possibility for military conflict","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"should the talks ultimately fail ,","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"Obama said ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"\" I welcome a robust debate . \"","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"Netanyahu ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"speaking several hours after the deal was announced ,","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"\" The concessions","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"offered to Iran in Lausanne","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"would ensure a bad deal","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"that would endanger Israel , the Middle East and the peace of the world .","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"Now is the time","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"for the international community to insist on a better deal . \"","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"House Speaker John Boehner ,","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"who has been on a trip to the Middle East ,","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"questioned elements of the deal","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"related to sanctions relief .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"The Republican insisted :","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"\" It would be naive to suggest","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"the Iranian regime will not continue to use its nuclear program , and any economic relief ,","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"to further destabilize the region . \"","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"Obama said","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"he saw three options :","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"The first , the U.S. ' current path of a negotiated agreement with Iran .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"Second , bombing Iran ' s nuclear facilities , a move","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"he warned","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"would set its program back only \" by a few years. \"","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"The third option ,","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"Obama said ,","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"was to \" pull out of negotiations ...","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"and hope for the best . \"","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"\" Iran is not going to dismantle its program","depth":14},{"id":64,"text":"because we demand it do so , \"","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"he said .","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"\" That ' s not how the world works . \"","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"Obama said","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"he had already called Saudi Arabia ' s King Salman before his Rose Garden speech .","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"But Obama did not call Netanyahu until well after his remarks","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"- during a flight to Louisville , Kentucky , aboard Air Force One .","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"According to the White House ,","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"the president told Netanyahu","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"the deal \" in no way diminishes our concerns with respect to Iran ' s sponsorship of terrorism and threats towards Israel. \"","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"Obama also directed his national security team to \" increase consultations \" with the Israeli government .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"The Israeli readout of the call said","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"that Netanyahu stressed","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"that the deal would threaten Israel ' s existence .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"The agreement itself was announced in Lausanne by European Union foreign policy chief Federica Mogherini and Iranian Foreign Minister Javad Zarif .","depth":5},{"id":79,"text":"What was laid out Thursday was essentially a broad a framework ;","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"a more comprehensive , technical deal is expected by June 30 .","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"Still , the result caught many close observers by surprise","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"after reports from the shores of Lake Geneva suggested","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"talks were heading toward a vague press statement of principles - or outright impasse .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"\" I was expecting either no agreement today or a much thinner one , \"","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"said Richard N. Haass , president of the Council on Foreign Relations .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"\" It is more substantive and more comprehensive","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"than many us thought would be the case . \"","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"Haass specifically praised the extent of monitoring of the nuclear supply chain and concessions on the number of centrifuges .","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"But","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"given the amount of work","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"to be done before June 30 ,","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"\" no one should be popping champagne today , \"","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"Haass cautioned .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"\" For all","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"we know ,","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"there will be backtracking . \"","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"- Iran will dismantle two-thirds of its 19,000 installed centrifuges .","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"Those devices ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"which spin uranium into material","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"that can be used for a nuclear weapon ,","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"will be stored under International Atomic Energy Agency oversight .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"Tehran will be left with 6,104 centrifuges , lower than some reported offers by the U.S. ,","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"and 5,060 of those can be used","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"to enrich uranium .","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"- Iran can keep open an underground nuclear facility at Fordow , a controversial site","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"because it was built in secret","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"and only revealed by the U.S. in 2009 .","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"Iran will not be required to close the facility","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"but could use it only for research","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"that does not include the enrichment of uranium .","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"- Rigorous transparency and inspection measures","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"to ensure","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"that Iran doesn ' t cheat on any deal .","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"They include granting the IAEA intrusive access to Iran ' s nuclear facilities and supply chain , including to its domestic uranium mines and mills .","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"The inspections would continue","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"even after many elements of the deal have expired in 2025 ,","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"including surveillance of Iran ' s centrifuge rotors until 2035 .","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"Iran has also agreed to some indefinite transparency measures .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"- In return for the limits on Iran ' s program , the U.S. and EU will suspend sanctions","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"after the IAEA has verified Iran ' s compliance with the deal ;","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"those sanctions can automatically \" snap back \"","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"if Iran violates the agreement at any time .","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"( Obama can temporarily suspend sanctions","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"passed by Congress ,","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"although only Congress can permanently repeal them . )","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"The United Nations will also lift its sanctions on Iran","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"after it meets the deal ' s requirements .","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"Speak","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"ng in Lausanne ,","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"ecretary of State John Kerry called the framework \" a critical milestone \" and \" a solid foundation for the good deal","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"e are seeking . \"","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"he exact timing of sanctions relief ,","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"e noted ,","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"remains one of those issues","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"hat is going to be negotiated over the course of the next three months. \"","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"n general ,","depth":15},{"id":137,"text":"e said ,","depth":15},{"id":138,"text":"Iran has the responsibility","depth":15},{"id":139,"text":"o get the breakout time to one year \"","depth":15},{"id":140,"text":"meaning it has to prove to the satisfaction of international inspectors","depth":14},{"id":141,"text":"hat it would take at least a year to develop a nuclear weapon ,","depth":15},{"id":142,"text":"o there would be plenty of advance warning","depth":16},{"id":143,"text":"f Iran tried to do that .","depth":16},{"id":144,"text":"nce IAEA inspectors certify","depth":15},{"id":145,"text":"hat Iran has met those conditions ,","depth":15},{"id":146,"text":"erry said ,","depth":14},{"id":147,"text":"anctions will begin to be reduced .","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"he deal ,","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"ey points of which were sent out to reporters by the White House ,","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"as unclear on some crucial questions","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"hat critics are sure to pounce on :","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"Although the agreement specifies","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"hat Iran will dramatically \" reduce \" its current stockpile of low-enriched uranium by 97 percent , from 10,000 kilograms to 300 kilograms ,","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"etails of the agreement","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"rovided by the Obama administration","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"o not say","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"ow that will happen .","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":".S. officials are expected to require Iran to ship that material","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"which is more than halfway to the potency","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"eeded for a bomb -","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"ut of the country .","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"ut Iran has proposed to retain the material","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"nd simply dilute it to a form unsuitable for a nuclear weapon ,","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"lthough that dilution is reversible .","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"erry , however , said in Lausanne","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"hat negotiators have a resolution on what to do with Iran ' s uranium :","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"It has to be either diluted","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"r sold on the international market , one of the two . ... That is agreed upon at this point in time , \"","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"e said .","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"Iran has refused to answer a list of IAEA questions about its suspected past research into nuclear weapons technology , like explosives","depth":8},{"id":171,"text":"hat can detonate highly enriched uranium .","depth":8},{"id":172,"text":"he agreement does not specify","depth":10},{"id":173,"text":"ow or when that will happen ,","depth":10},{"id":174,"text":"aying only","depth":10},{"id":175,"text":"hat \" Iran will implement an agreed set of measures","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"o address the IAEA ' s concerns \" on the military research question .","depth":11},{"id":177,"text":"ogherini said only","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"hat the nuclear agency \" will have enhanced access through agreed procedures ,","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"ncluding to clarify past and present issues . \"","depth":10},{"id":180,"text":"il-rich Iran has long insisted","depth":4},{"id":181,"text":"ts nuclear program is for scientific , medical and other purposes ,","depth":5},{"id":182,"text":"ot for making weapons .","depth":5},{"id":183,"text":"n Thursday , Zarif said","depth":7},{"id":184,"text":"ran has agreed to take steps","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"o assure the world","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"that our program is exclusively peaceful ,","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"hat our program always has been and always will be exclusively peaceful. \"","depth":11},{"id":188,"text":"ut ,","depth":11},{"id":189,"text":"e added ,","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"ran will not close any of its nuclear facilities","depth":10},{"id":191,"text":"a condition","depth":11},{"id":192,"text":"t said","depth":11},{"id":193,"text":"ould have been unacceptable .","depth":10},{"id":194,"text":"We have done significant work .","depth":8},{"id":195,"text":"e have made achievements .","depth":9},{"id":196,"text":"e have made progress , \"","depth":9},{"id":197,"text":"arif said .","depth":7},{"id":198,"text":"bama stressed in particular the inspection and verification aspects of the agreement .","depth":9},{"id":199,"text":"If Iran cheats ,","depth":13},{"id":200,"text":"he world will know it .","depth":13},{"id":201,"text":"f we see anything suspicious ,","depth":13},{"id":202,"text":"e will inspect it , \"","depth":13},{"id":203,"text":"bama said .","depth":11},{"id":204,"text":"e said","depth":11},{"id":205,"text":"ran will face \" more inspections than any other country in the world. \"","depth":11},{"id":206,"text":"nd he said","depth":9},{"id":207,"text":"he relief from sanctions will be \" phased \"","depth":10},{"id":208,"text":"s long as Iran proves","depth":11},{"id":209,"text":"t is complying with the terms of an agreement .","depth":11},{"id":210,"text":"If there is backsliding on the part of the Iranians , \"","depth":9},{"id":211,"text":"e said ,","depth":9},{"id":212,"text":"there will be no deal . \"","depth":8},{"id":213,"text":"erry contended","depth":9},{"id":214,"text":"hat the deal has no sunset date .","depth":9},{"id":215,"text":"n reality , most of its provisions","depth":10},{"id":216,"text":"how many centrifuges Iran can run , for instance -","depth":10},{"id":217,"text":"ill expire after a decade .","depth":9},{"id":218,"text":"ut Iran has agreed to a special arrangement with the IAEA","depth":8},{"id":219,"text":"nown as the Additional Protocol ,","depth":10},{"id":220,"text":"hich grants the international agency ' s inspectors enhanced information about and access to the country ' s nuclear activities and infrastructure .","depth":10},{"id":221,"text":"he Additional Protocol has no time limit .","depth":9},{"id":222,"text":"he deal ' s announcement came after a final round of negotiations in Lausanne ,","depth":6},{"id":223,"text":"ollowing a grueling marathon session","depth":8},{"id":224,"text":"hat kept officials talking until 6 a.m. Thursday","depth":8},{"id":225,"text":"and two days after a self-imposed deadline","depth":8},{"id":226,"text":"o reach a political agreement .","depth":8},{"id":227,"text":"side from the U.S. and Iran , countries participating include Germany , France , Britain , Russia and China .","depth":5},{"id":228,"text":"arlier this week , the Obama administration started signaling its impatience with the Iranians ,","depth":6},{"id":229,"text":"ith White House press secretary Josh Earnest warning Wednesday","depth":7},{"id":230,"text":"hat the negotiations would not be \" open-ended. \"","depth":7},{"id":231,"text":"he Iranians also dug in ,","depth":6},{"id":232,"text":"epeatedly pointing to sanctions relief as a major concern .","depth":6},{"id":233,"text":"he agreement could end up at the mercy of U.S. domestic politics ,","depth":6},{"id":234,"text":"nd it was fast fodder for Republicans","depth":7},{"id":235,"text":"oping to succeed Obama in the White House .","depth":7},{"id":236,"text":"This attempt","depth":8},{"id":237,"text":"o spin diplomatic failure as a success","depth":8},{"id":238,"text":"s just the latest example of this administration ' s farcical approach to Iran , \"","depth":7},{"id":239,"text":"lorida Sen. Marco Rubio ,","depth":8},{"id":240,"text":"ho is expected to announce his bid for the Republican nomination this month ,","depth":8},{"id":241,"text":"aid in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":242,"text":"ongressional leaders also insist","depth":7},{"id":243,"text":"hey want a say in any deal .","depth":7},{"id":244,"text":"OP Sen. Bob Corker , chairman of the Senate Foreign Relations Committee , said","depth":8},{"id":245,"text":"t was \" important that we wait to see the specific details , \"","depth":8},{"id":246,"text":"ut he did not back away from his pledge","depth":8},{"id":247,"text":"o pass bipartisan legislation","depth":9},{"id":248,"text":"iving Congress the right","depth":10},{"id":249,"text":"o block an accord .","depth":10},{"id":250,"text":"poll out Monday showed","depth":7},{"id":251,"text":"hat 49 percent of Americans support the talks ,","depth":8},{"id":252,"text":"hile 40 percent disapprove .","depth":8},{"id":253,"text":"bout two-thirds of respondents to the Pew Research Center poll do not think","depth":7},{"id":254,"text":"ran is serious about \" addressing nuclear concerns . \"","depth":7},{"id":255,"text":"any Iranians ,","depth":7},{"id":256,"text":"ho have watched their economy wobble underneath international sanctions ,","depth":7},{"id":257,"text":"ere thrilled over the deal .","depth":6},{"id":258,"text":"hotos from Iranian and Western outlets showed","depth":7},{"id":259,"text":"oung Iranian men and women","depth":8},{"id":260,"text":"heering in the roads","depth":9},{"id":261,"text":"nd flashing victory signs from their cars Thursday evening .","depth":9},{"id":262,"text":"ut there were also signs of discontent among Iranian hardliners .","depth":7},{"id":263,"text":"ccording to Iran ' s semi-official Fars News Agency ,","depth":9},{"id":264,"text":"ossein Shariatmadari , editor of the conservative Kayhan newspaper , declared of the deal :","depth":9},{"id":265,"text":"We gave them a saddled horse in return for some broken reins . \"","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":531,"left":445,"right":530,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":445,"left":278,"right":444,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":270,"right":277,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":270,"left":0,"right":269,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":2